<parameterdescription>
<para>API list. See <ref refid="structlog__link__api" kindref="compound">log_link_api</ref>. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>_buf_wlen</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Size (in words) of dedicated buffer for messages from this buffer. If 0 default buffer is used. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
